  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "Verse 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Once my soul was astray from the heavenly way,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 33
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 42
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And was wretched and vile as could be;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 35
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "But my Saviour above, gave me peace, joy and love,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 30
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 45
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When He reached down His hand for me, for me.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 25
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 34
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "chorus",
    "label" : "Chorus",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "When He reached down His hand for me; (2)",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 34
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I was lost and undone, without God or His Son,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 31
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 42
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When He reached down His hand for me, for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "Verse 2",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "I was nearing despair, when He came to me there,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 31
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 42
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And He showed me that I could be free;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Then He lifted my feet, gave me glory complete,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 32
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "When He reached down His hand for me, for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "Verse 3",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "How my heart doth rejoice since I made Him my choice,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 34
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 46
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "From the tempest to Him now I flee;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 30
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Now I lean on His arm, I'm secure from all harm,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 29
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 43
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Since He reached down His hand for me, for me.",
      "chords" : [ {
